The MiniMail distribution may be spread freely without profit, as long as none of the included files are modified, replaced or left out. Modified versions may exist for your personal use, but do not spread them. Different archivers, compressors and encoding schemes may of course be applied without restrictions. It may not be featured on any coverdisks without my written permission. All other kinds of distribution, like through AmiNet or BBSes, are @{B}encouraged@{UB}!
